WEBVTT

00:13.430 --> 00:15.030
By decree of the King of Great Yan:

00:15.030 --> 00:18.120
Consort Helian of Great Yan,
virtuous by nature,

00:18.320 --> 00:19.600
diligent, and gentle,

00:20.440 --> 00:24.100
is hereby elevated to Queen of Great Yan,
effective immediately.

00:30.390 --> 00:32.430
Huo Sang, elder of the Baichuan Tribe,
hails from a lineage

00:32.430 --> 00:34.000
that has been loyal and valiant
for generations.

00:34.000 --> 00:36.790
His daughter, Baichuan—virtuous, gentle,

00:36.960 --> 00:38.640
and accomplished in
both character and talent—

00:38.640 --> 00:41.350
is hereby granted the title of Consort.

00:41.790 --> 00:44.640
The daughter of the Elder of the Pale Tribe
is hereby appointed Consort,

00:44.640 --> 00:47.670
with the three cities
of Linchuan, Shazhou, and Jiuhe

00:47.960 --> 00:49.690
bestowed as her personal fief!

00:50.280 --> 00:53.210
-Thank you, Your Majesty!
-Thank you, Your Majesty!

02:16.180 --> 02:21.450
[REBIRTH]

02:21.910 --> 02:24.430
[Episode 38]

04:35.040 --> 04:35.920
Chu!

04:37.270 --> 04:40.000
I'll marry you
and make you the Queen of Great Yan.

04:40.510 --> 04:42.840
I'll take you to ride Mount Huihui horses.

04:46.159 --> 04:47.040
Chu...

04:51.020 --> 04:53.230
♪ The flowers fall into the sleeves ♪

04:53.659 --> 04:56.200
♪ They do not understand my sorrow ♪

04:56.320 --> 04:57.620
♪ With a pot of wine ♪

04:57.650 --> 04:59.110
♪ My longing surges ♪

04:59.130 --> 05:01.640
♪ I become haggard ♪

05:02.250 --> 05:04.690
♪ Soft rain patters on the windowpane ♪

05:04.740 --> 05:07.560
♪ Awakening from the dream,
I no longer know what year it is ♪

05:07.580 --> 05:09.280
♪ My love remains ♪

05:09.590 --> 05:12.960
♪ But you're already gone ♪

05:12.990 --> 05:15.260
♪ What I seek in life ♪

05:15.280 --> 05:16.870
♪ Is nothing more
than to look back once more ♪

05:16.890 --> 05:19.480
♪ With the fragrance still lingering ♪

05:19.500 --> 05:21.090
♪ In these trembling hands ♪

05:21.110 --> 05:24.300
♪ My longing still rests ♪

05:24.320 --> 05:26.680
♪ Words left unspoken ♪

05:26.710 --> 05:28.220
♪ Turn into guilt ♪

05:28.240 --> 05:30.900
♪ Beneath the stars ♪

05:30.920 --> 05:35.780
♪ Rippling throughout this life ♪

05:35.810 --> 05:37.200
♪ I ask the vast sky ♪

05:37.230 --> 05:39.480
♪ The wind is light,
but my longing is heavy ♪

05:39.500 --> 05:41.950
♪ How do we start over? ♪

05:41.970 --> 05:45.280
♪ How do we love
and hold on without parting ♪

05:45.310 --> 05:47.560
♪ Or misunderstanding each other? ♪

05:47.590 --> 05:51.000
♪ Do not let me only understand
the meaning of a fleeting glance ♪

05:51.020 --> 05:53.340
♪ When my eyes are red with tears ♪

05:53.360 --> 05:56.240
♪ What cannot be kept,
can only be sent away ♪

05:56.270 --> 06:00.810
♪ In the end ♪

07:44.870 --> 07:45.630
Helian.

07:47.630 --> 07:49.560
Thank you for being willing to help me.

07:49.560 --> 07:50.360
Your Majesty.

07:52.390 --> 07:54.650
Since childhood, I've dreamed of one day

07:56.130 --> 07:57.930
becoming the queen of Great Yan.

07:58.360 --> 07:59.159
Only this way

08:00.920 --> 08:02.720
could I bring honor to our tribe,

08:03.480 --> 08:05.430
stop my brother from bullying me,

08:06.310 --> 08:09.170
and protect my clansmen from
further humiliation.

08:09.920 --> 08:10.950
So today

08:12.390 --> 08:14.560
is the day my wish comes true.

08:16.120 --> 08:17.600
I am very happy.

08:20.560 --> 08:21.270
Tomorrow,

08:23.270 --> 08:25.310
the troops of
the Pale and the Baichuan Tribes

08:25.310 --> 08:26.630
will arrive here.

08:27.680 --> 08:28.560
In three days,

08:29.750 --> 08:31.610
I will lead the campaign to Ximeng

08:32.840 --> 08:34.200
to fight the Yong Army.

08:36.320 --> 08:37.780
Your Majesty once said...

08:40.600 --> 08:43.200
you hoped I could become your ally—

08:43.890 --> 08:45.560
someone useful to Great Yan.

08:51.150 --> 08:52.480
Have I done so?

09:01.510 --> 09:02.150
You have.

10:37.760 --> 10:38.760
Your Majesty!

10:46.910 --> 10:50.080
All 10,000 Baichuan troops are assembled!

10:51.030 --> 10:54.480
All 9,000 Pale troops are assembled!

10:55.440 --> 10:58.720
All 6,000 Helian soldiers are assembled!

10:59.910 --> 11:02.240
15,000 from the Black Eagle Army

11:02.600 --> 11:04.530
and 12,000 from the Great Yan Army—

11:04.790 --> 11:06.870
totaling 52,000 troops—

11:07.240 --> 11:09.300
have all assembled outside the city,

11:09.510 --> 11:11.370
awaiting Your Majesty's orders!

11:27.910 --> 11:28.720
Your Majesty!

12:02.240 --> 12:03.040
Your Majesty,

12:03.480 --> 12:06.080
please take this sword with you
on the campaign

12:06.480 --> 12:08.240
and protect Great Yan with it.

12:08.600 --> 12:10.330
This was General Cheng's wish.

12:13.720 --> 12:15.080
And General Cheng would once again

12:15.080 --> 12:17.440
bring Your Majesty back safely.

12:31.750 --> 12:32.630
I promise you.

12:36.320 --> 12:39.550
I will uphold Cheng Yuan's will
to protect the land

12:41.390 --> 12:42.750
and return safely.

12:43.310 --> 12:50.830
♪ The lonely black eagle ♪

12:52.310 --> 12:55.640
♪ Is flying against the light ♪

12:56.460 --> 12:59.650
♪ Where is my hometown? ♪

13:00.190 --> 13:09.150
♪ In the vast world ♪

13:09.180 --> 13:12.580
♪ I have no origin ♪

13:12.270 --> 13:14.550
March!

13:13.240 --> 13:16.830
♪ And no destination ♪

13:14.960 --> 13:16.070
Yes!

13:16.360 --> 13:20.390
Yes! Yes! Yes!

13:17.400 --> 13:25.450
♪ A pair of stubborn wings ♪

13:20.720 --> 13:23.270
Yes! Yes! Yes!

13:25.670 --> 13:33.940
♪ Is born to fly ♪

14:24.750 --> 14:26.960
I, Chu Qiao,
daughter of Great Yong's Emperor,

14:26.960 --> 14:30.080
hereby present the jade seal
and military tally of Ximeng,

14:30.080 --> 14:32.080
pledge my allegiance to Great Yong,

14:32.200 --> 14:34.000
and will never break the treaty.

15:04.870 --> 15:05.440
Guards!

15:08.620 --> 15:09.820
Chu Qiao is a witch.

15:10.330 --> 15:11.750
She has angered
the ancestors of Great Yong

15:11.750 --> 15:13.200
and brought down heavenly fire.

15:13.200 --> 15:14.080
Seize her!

15:15.440 --> 15:16.230
Nobody move!

15:17.360 --> 15:18.150
Step back.

15:18.910 --> 15:19.600
Stand down.

15:44.030 --> 15:46.160
Ministers, there is no need for panic.

15:46.270 --> 15:48.440
There is no such thing as "heavenly fire."

15:48.440 --> 15:50.790
What caused the portrait
to burn on its own was,

15:50.790 --> 15:52.270
in fact, flint powder.

15:56.510 --> 15:57.960
What is flint powder?

15:58.120 --> 16:01.000
It's a substance
that can spontaneously ignite.

16:01.440 --> 16:04.200
When exposed to strong sunlight
and rising temperatures,

16:04.200 --> 16:05.720
it will catch fire on its own.

16:05.720 --> 16:08.150
The fire seen that day
at the Jiuyou Platform

16:08.150 --> 16:09.680
was caused by flint powder.

16:09.910 --> 16:10.670
Zhao Che

16:11.510 --> 16:13.440
has been using the Faceless God Sect

16:13.440 --> 16:15.840
and flint powder to fool you all!

16:20.510 --> 16:21.320
Nonsense!

16:21.670 --> 16:24.270
The Faceless God Sect is
the sacred religion of Great Yong—

16:24.270 --> 16:25.600
how dare you slander it!

16:25.870 --> 16:28.240
You've been using its name

16:28.750 --> 16:30.150
to eliminate your political rivals.

16:30.150 --> 16:32.080
Muhe Lie, Wei Guang,

16:32.360 --> 16:33.820
and the late General Meng—

16:34.270 --> 16:35.910
were all murdered simply because they

16:35.910 --> 16:37.150
were not his cronies.

16:38.800 --> 16:42.950
How could the Crown Prince
commit such a treasonous act?

16:43.790 --> 16:45.030
If you don't believe it,

16:45.030 --> 16:48.150
order an immediate search of
the secret passage beneath the ancestral temple.

16:48.150 --> 16:50.510
Mu Shen confessed before his death.

16:51.080 --> 16:53.910
On Zhao Che's orders, he used
the temple renovations as a pretext

16:53.910 --> 16:55.320
to hide large quantities of flint powder

16:55.320 --> 16:57.000
in the secret passage.

17:00.510 --> 17:01.550
Xing Le.

17:02.150 --> 17:03.030
Yes, Your Majesty!

17:03.030 --> 17:03.870
Search!

17:04.270 --> 17:04.790
Yes!

17:15.369 --> 17:17.020
[Chengde Hall]

17:23.069 --> 17:24.730
There really is flint powder.

17:29.070 --> 17:29.790
Father,

17:31.240 --> 17:34.000
this is Chu Qiao's scheme to frame me.

17:34.240 --> 17:35.200
Mu Shen is dead.

17:36.200 --> 17:39.660
How can she prove that the powder
was placed there on my orders?

17:41.400 --> 17:42.030
Father.

17:43.920 --> 17:46.920
This woman Chu Qiao
harbors treacherous intentions.

17:47.000 --> 17:48.600
She's colluded with Yan Xun,

17:49.070 --> 17:51.310
seeking to throw our court into chaos.

17:51.790 --> 17:54.110
Every move of her has been
a calculated scheme!

17:54.110 --> 17:56.370
Father, you must not fall for her scheme.

18:08.240 --> 18:09.000
Your Majesty,

18:09.000 --> 18:09.920
Your Highness,

18:10.070 --> 18:11.350
urgent report from the frontier—

18:11.350 --> 18:14.720
the armies of Great Yan and Ximeng
have split into several forces

18:14.720 --> 18:16.650
and are heading toward our border.

18:17.160 --> 18:18.720
This.... This is bad.

18:25.240 --> 18:25.880
Father,

18:26.510 --> 18:29.160
this is precisely
Chu Qiao and Yan Xun's conspiracy.

18:29.160 --> 18:31.020
She falsely accuses me here today

18:31.510 --> 18:33.750
just to drive a wedge between us,

18:34.110 --> 18:35.910
plunging Great Yong into chaos.

18:36.070 --> 18:37.960
And Yan Xun seizes this opportunity
to dispatch troops,

18:37.960 --> 18:40.760
forcing our state
to face attacks from both sides!

18:45.880 --> 18:48.540
Now, the empire stands on
the brink of collapse.

18:48.790 --> 18:50.720
At this moment of national crisis,

18:51.160 --> 18:53.640
will you believe Chu Qiao, a witch,

18:54.160 --> 18:54.920
or me,

18:54.940 --> 18:57.260
the future heir of Great Yong?

19:02.400 --> 19:03.400
Guards,

19:04.160 --> 19:06.240
seize the witch Chu Qiao

19:06.240 --> 19:07.590
and throw her in prison!

19:08.770 --> 19:09.430
Don't move!

19:10.480 --> 19:11.790
Move, and I'll kill him!

19:11.790 --> 19:12.450
Don't move.

19:15.510 --> 19:18.110
Witch Chu Qiao,
in collusion with General Xing Le,

19:18.110 --> 19:19.440
has framed the Crown Prince

19:19.440 --> 19:20.770
and misled the Emperor!

19:20.920 --> 19:22.380
Her crimes deserve death!

19:22.910 --> 19:24.300
Execute her on the spot!

19:29.990 --> 19:30.920
Your Majesty...

19:31.000 --> 19:31.930
Your Majesty...

19:43.680 --> 19:44.840
Zhuge Yue.

19:51.000 --> 19:51.920
You...

20:02.790 --> 20:04.390
His Majesty has passed away.

20:04.590 --> 20:07.510
From this moment on,
the Crown Prince is the new Emperor.

20:07.510 --> 20:09.910
All shall obey the Crown Prince's command!

20:09.920 --> 20:12.640
Witch Chu Qiao,
together with the traitor Xing Le,

20:12.640 --> 20:14.310
has committed regicide and rebellion.

20:14.310 --> 20:15.680
Seize them both!

20:16.430 --> 20:16.910
Let go!

20:22.750 --> 20:23.750
Who dares to move?

20:25.880 --> 20:26.720
Huan Huan.

20:32.180 --> 20:34.110
Let Chu Qiao and General Xing Le go!

20:34.510 --> 20:35.970
Otherwise, I'll kill you!

20:36.270 --> 20:37.000
Huan Huan...

20:38.720 --> 20:39.750
Don't force me.

20:41.070 --> 20:42.530
Do I need to say that again?

20:43.030 --> 20:43.880
Let them go!

20:49.510 --> 20:50.170
Step aside!

20:53.550 --> 20:54.150
Huan Huan.

20:55.030 --> 20:56.030
Come with us.

20:56.790 --> 20:57.440
Chu Qiao,

20:57.880 --> 20:59.030
Yan Xun's army and Ximeng's army

20:59.030 --> 21:00.400
are already on their way.

21:00.400 --> 21:02.110
Do you want us all to die here?

21:02.440 --> 21:03.170
General Chu,

21:03.830 --> 21:04.590
let's go.

21:05.200 --> 21:05.750
Hurry.

21:18.960 --> 21:19.750
Huan Huan,

21:20.720 --> 21:22.160
why do you force my hand?

21:25.160 --> 21:26.350
You know—

21:27.750 --> 21:29.440
better than anyone—

21:29.440 --> 21:30.590
I have no choice!

21:31.880 --> 21:33.140
As long as you stop now,

21:34.270 --> 21:35.550
it's not too late.

21:38.110 --> 21:40.240
And if I don't...

21:43.880 --> 21:45.160
you will kill me,

21:46.070 --> 21:46.880
right?

21:48.160 --> 21:48.880
Yes.

21:51.440 --> 21:52.240
Huan Huan,

21:54.070 --> 21:56.200
from the day you and I were ambushed

21:56.200 --> 21:57.600
in the woods of Great Yan,

21:57.790 --> 21:59.920
from the day you accompanied me
to Yan County

21:59.920 --> 22:02.000
to rally my troops—

22:02.400 --> 22:04.460
there has been no turning back for me.

22:05.110 --> 22:05.720
No,

22:06.440 --> 22:07.350
there is.

22:09.160 --> 22:09.960
I know

22:10.070 --> 22:12.590
you are not a man
consumed by greed and ambition.

22:12.590 --> 22:14.350
I know there is goodness in you.

22:15.270 --> 22:17.130
The endless warfare of Great Yong

22:17.440 --> 22:19.300
is not what you want to see either.

22:20.240 --> 22:20.920
Zhao Che.

22:22.240 --> 22:23.480
Let go of all this...

22:24.920 --> 22:25.880
and come with me.

22:27.880 --> 22:31.790
Let's restore peace
to Great Yong and Great Yan.

22:32.310 --> 22:34.170
We can call a truce and make peace,

22:35.550 --> 22:39.000
just as your father
and the old King of Great Yan once did.

22:41.720 --> 22:42.440
Then...

22:44.510 --> 22:45.920
we can leave together,

22:47.070 --> 22:47.790
okay?

22:51.550 --> 22:52.270
Okay.

23:42.620 --> 23:44.880
Zhuge Yue, Prince of Jing, hear my order—

23:46.270 --> 23:49.130
surround General Xing Le's residence
immediately

23:49.200 --> 23:52.130
and launch a citywide manhunt
for the witch Chu Qiao.

23:52.750 --> 23:53.310
Yes.

23:55.240 --> 23:55.790
Yes.

24:08.590 --> 24:09.400
Huan Huan,

24:09.900 --> 24:11.380
you were still too naive.

24:14.660 --> 24:17.320
This world was never meant
for someone like you.

25:17.350 --> 25:18.200
General Xing,

25:19.960 --> 25:22.620
what's the situation
with Great Yan and Ximeng?

25:23.830 --> 25:25.440
My men just sent word—

25:26.160 --> 25:29.030
Great Yan's army has broken through

25:29.030 --> 25:31.490
the border of Great Yong
from the southwest.

25:31.680 --> 25:34.590
The Yong Army has been forced
to retreat from Ximeng Pass

25:34.590 --> 25:38.000
and is rerouting via the Yuan River
to reinforce the southwestern frontier.

25:38.000 --> 25:38.830
Moreover,

25:38.920 --> 25:40.830
Biantang has also dispatched troops.

25:40.830 --> 25:42.960
General Sun Di is leading 50,000 soldiers

25:42.960 --> 25:45.110
to join forces with Great Yan and Ximeng

25:45.110 --> 25:46.510
to advance on Great Yong.

25:49.160 --> 25:49.960
Are our men

25:51.000 --> 25:52.110
ready?

25:52.790 --> 25:54.550
I've gathered

25:54.550 --> 25:56.640
all the trusted troops I could mobilize—

25:56.640 --> 25:57.640
a total of 100 men.

25:57.960 --> 25:59.790
They're assembled at Shili Hill
outside the city,

25:59.790 --> 26:01.050
awaiting your orders.

26:01.200 --> 26:02.060
One hundred men

26:03.400 --> 26:04.270
are enough.

26:23.830 --> 26:25.290
That's Zhao Che's, right?

26:31.590 --> 26:35.210
♪ The dust in the world ♪

26:33.160 --> 26:35.000
We met in Baige Town in Great Yan.

26:35.730 --> 26:39.200
♪ Is blown away easily by the wind ♪

26:37.160 --> 26:39.090
I didn't know who he was at the time.

26:39.910 --> 26:42.710
♪ Who can stay calm ♪

26:40.200 --> 26:43.270
After I returned to Great Yan,
I found him framed

26:43.510 --> 26:44.680
and already wounded
from being hunted down.

26:43.540 --> 26:44.890
♪ And not be scared? ♪

26:44.910 --> 26:46.930
♪ A slight ripple ♪

26:45.070 --> 26:47.270
He asked me to escort him
to rejoin his old subordinates.

26:47.110 --> 26:50.700
♪ Floating life hangs by a thread ♪

26:50.720 --> 26:51.750
But I never imagined

26:50.990 --> 26:54.350
♪ The more pulled, the softer it gets ♪

26:52.440 --> 26:54.920
he would bring his troops back
to Zhenhuangcheng

26:54.920 --> 26:56.200
just for this day.

26:55.320 --> 26:58.170
♪ Who dares to say forever? ♪

26:58.830 --> 27:02.200
♪ Let it be ♪

27:03.280 --> 27:06.710
♪ Grudges and grace
were never meant to be ♪

27:07.030 --> 27:08.000
I'll be using a sword tomorrow,

27:07.190 --> 27:10.200
♪ Why must you take and demand so much? ♪

27:08.480 --> 27:10.480
and wearing this will get in the way.

27:10.580 --> 27:12.210
♪ Go weaving ♪

27:12.160 --> 27:13.110
Won't you regret it?

27:12.540 --> 27:17.500
♪ Grand and glorious excuses ♪

27:17.070 --> 27:18.070
We made a pact long ago—

27:18.010 --> 27:20.810
♪ We once beheld ♪

27:19.240 --> 27:20.370
the next time we met,

27:20.830 --> 27:24.240
♪ A mirage on earth ♪

27:21.680 --> 27:22.880
we'd only be enemies.

27:25.960 --> 27:28.600
♪ Beauty never ♪

27:28.620 --> 27:33.350
♪ Lasts for long ♪

27:33.620 --> 27:37.140
♪ No matter how a jade is carved ♪

27:37.170 --> 27:41.600
♪ It's just a stone ♪

27:41.920 --> 27:49.130
♪ It will eventually disappear ♪

27:50.290 --> 28:01.550
♪ It will eventually disappear ♪

28:14.350 --> 28:16.810
The sword pierced Your Highness's abdomen,

28:17.110 --> 28:18.590
striking

28:19.070 --> 28:21.310
the child in the womb.

28:22.070 --> 28:23.920
Your Highness's life is not in danger,

28:23.920 --> 28:24.830
but

28:25.580 --> 28:27.380
the child cannot be saved.

29:24.000 --> 29:24.800
Your Majesty,

29:25.640 --> 29:26.680
Great Yan's army

29:26.830 --> 29:29.290
has already breached our southwest border.

29:29.310 --> 29:30.830
Our troops at Ximeng Pass

29:31.070 --> 29:33.200
have been dispatched to
reinforce the southwest.

29:33.200 --> 29:34.200
But this leaves

29:34.830 --> 29:37.160
the northwest frontier
dangerously underdefended.

29:37.160 --> 29:39.160
If the Ximeng Army
takes this chance to attack,

29:39.160 --> 29:41.290
we may be caught completely off guard!

29:43.400 --> 29:44.400
What should we do?

29:48.110 --> 29:49.400
Pass down my orders—

29:49.960 --> 29:52.880
send troops to
reinforce Ximeng Pass at once.

29:53.160 --> 29:53.960
Your Majesty,

29:54.030 --> 29:55.880
our forces are already stretched thin.

29:55.880 --> 29:58.210
The remaining men must guard the capital.

29:58.310 --> 30:00.830
If we draw more soldiers
from the capital now,

30:00.830 --> 30:02.760
it will only invite further chaos!

30:04.070 --> 30:05.800
How far have Great Yan's forces

30:06.000 --> 30:06.920
advanced?

30:07.270 --> 30:09.160
They've already reached Ling County.

30:09.160 --> 30:10.750
Once they cross the Luanxi River,

30:10.750 --> 30:12.150
it will truly be too late!

30:16.750 --> 30:17.480
Brother!

30:22.880 --> 30:24.340
There is only one way left.

30:28.270 --> 30:31.880
The Quanrong people in the northwest
are burly and skilled in battle.

30:31.880 --> 30:35.030
Please, Your Majesty, propose
a marriage alliance with the Quanrong,

30:35.030 --> 30:37.830
offering me in return for
their military support.

30:37.880 --> 30:38.750
That way,

30:39.000 --> 30:41.350
we can quell the crisis on our border.

30:42.510 --> 30:43.710
A marriage alliance?

30:50.640 --> 30:52.160
Sending the Princess to a foreign land

30:52.160 --> 30:54.510
would indeed secure military support,

30:55.510 --> 30:57.270
but this is truly humiliating!

30:57.270 --> 30:59.670
What would become of Great Yong's dignity?

30:59.680 --> 31:00.960
The state is

31:01.590 --> 31:03.070
on the brink of collapse!

31:03.790 --> 31:05.270
Which matters more—

31:05.830 --> 31:08.030
dignity, or the survival of the nation?

31:08.240 --> 31:10.000
Since the founding of Great Yong,

31:10.000 --> 31:10.720
there has never been

31:10.720 --> 31:13.070
a precedent for a princess
being married off to a foreign state.

31:13.070 --> 31:13.960
No precedent—

31:14.310 --> 31:15.840
so no exception can be made?

31:16.230 --> 31:17.310
It must not be done!

31:20.310 --> 31:21.830
It must not be done!

31:23.550 --> 31:24.350
Stop arguing!

31:35.100 --> 31:38.210
[Temple of the Faceless God]

31:48.400 --> 31:49.200
Your Majesty,

31:50.200 --> 31:52.310
are you really going to
send Princess Chun'er

31:52.310 --> 31:54.570
to the Quanrong for a marriage alliance?

31:56.030 --> 31:57.030
Why not?

31:58.480 --> 32:00.480
Jia Meng has come from the Quanrong.

32:00.880 --> 32:03.830
She's brought a state letter of
marriage alliance from their chieftain,

32:03.830 --> 32:06.430
offering 100,000 Quanrong troops
in support.

32:07.440 --> 32:09.310
The Quanrong are brutal

32:09.310 --> 32:10.680
and bloodthirsty by nature.

32:10.680 --> 32:13.310
For years, we have kept
our distance from them

32:13.440 --> 32:14.970
with virtually no contact.

32:15.160 --> 32:17.510
To trade the Princess
for their soldiers now—

32:17.510 --> 32:19.030
setting aside
whether those 100,000 troops

32:19.030 --> 32:20.440
would truly obey us—

32:20.750 --> 32:23.830
if they harbor any ulterior motives
and seize the opportunity to act,

32:23.830 --> 32:24.480
by the time

32:25.200 --> 32:26.310
we react,

32:26.960 --> 32:28.420
it may already be too late.

32:31.920 --> 32:32.750
Zhuge Yue,

32:33.920 --> 32:38.180
you oppose this marriage alliance
with the Quanrong in exchange for troops?

32:43.880 --> 32:45.080
Is it because you fear

32:45.880 --> 32:48.030
they may turn against us,

32:48.720 --> 32:51.450
or because you can't bear to
watch Ximeng perish,

32:51.680 --> 32:53.110
to see Chu Qiao die?

32:55.680 --> 32:56.480
Zhuge Yue,

32:56.880 --> 32:59.790
do you wish for Chu Qiao
and Great Yan to win,

33:00.440 --> 33:03.350
or do you want to go back to
being King Ximeng?

33:06.160 --> 33:08.350
There's something
I still haven't asked you—

33:08.350 --> 33:10.350
yesterday at the ancestral temple,

33:10.480 --> 33:13.000
you acted on your own
and killed the late Emperor.

33:13.000 --> 33:14.860
What exactly was your intention?

33:19.830 --> 33:20.750
I did so to

33:21.720 --> 33:23.590
get Your Highness
out of the dire situation.

33:23.590 --> 33:26.680
If you hadn't acted yesterday,

33:27.240 --> 33:29.880
Chu Qiao would never have
had the chance to escape.

33:29.880 --> 33:32.080
And I wouldn't have had to bear the crime

33:32.590 --> 33:35.250
of patricide and regicide
in front of everyone.

33:35.880 --> 33:36.750
Did you do that

33:37.480 --> 33:39.000
to help me

33:39.590 --> 33:41.240
or to help Chu Qiao leave?

33:41.920 --> 33:42.780
Your Highness,

33:43.640 --> 33:46.270
the late Emperor
had already discovered your plan.

33:46.270 --> 33:49.400
Pretending to believe you
was just a temporary measure.

33:49.920 --> 33:51.250
If we hadn't acted then,

33:52.000 --> 33:53.800
given his wariness and caution,

33:54.510 --> 33:56.510
the moment
he walked out of Tianyuan Palace,

33:56.510 --> 33:59.000
he would've tried everything
to turn the tables.

33:59.000 --> 33:59.830
By then,

34:00.750 --> 34:02.210
it would have been too late

34:02.270 --> 34:03.270
for us to act.

34:10.230 --> 34:11.030
Zhuge Yue,

34:12.190 --> 34:13.000
do you know?

34:13.670 --> 34:16.840
When the late Emperor successfully
inherited the throne,

34:16.840 --> 34:19.969
your grandfather Zhuge Muqing
rendered great service.

34:20.440 --> 34:21.840
Yet the late Emperor

34:22.320 --> 34:24.840
never regarded him
with the same suspicion and ruthlessness

34:24.840 --> 34:26.570
he showed toward Yan Shicheng.

34:27.510 --> 34:29.440
That was because your grandfather

34:29.510 --> 34:31.230
knew his place.

34:31.800 --> 34:33.360
He understood

34:33.960 --> 34:35.360
he stood beneath the sovereign.

34:35.360 --> 34:37.219
He would not interfere in matters

34:37.280 --> 34:38.739
that were not his concern.

34:39.440 --> 34:40.170
This subject

34:40.800 --> 34:41.600
understands.

35:10.770 --> 35:12.930
I want you to help me stop Zhao Che

35:13.140 --> 35:15.940
and completely transform
the realm of Great Yong.

35:16.030 --> 35:16.800
Today,

35:17.360 --> 35:19.290
I shall see who emerges victorious

35:20.290 --> 35:21.890
in this Faceless God Temple.

35:22.550 --> 35:24.670
Zhao Chun'er has opened the border gates

35:24.670 --> 35:26.600
and allowed the Quanrong to enter.

35:26.840 --> 35:28.170
I have made my decision—

35:29.280 --> 35:30.400
I shall lead the army
to face them in battle.
